The htk.patch file contains a patch to modify the HResults.c source 
to display a reformatted Confusion Matrix output.

Applying The Patch:
-------------------

$ mkdir tmp/
$ cp /*PATH*/*TO*/HTK-3.4.1.tar.gz tmp/
$ cd tmp/
$ tar -zxf HTK-3.4.1.tar.gz
$ cp /*PATH*/*TO*/htk_patches/htk.patch tmp/
$ patch -p0 < htk.patch


The HTK source (located in htk/) will be patched and can be built as normal.

